1
interests affected by product classification. Members appointed to
1
2
the Council shall serve at the pleasure of the Board. Appointees to
2
3
the Council shall serve for a term of five (5) years. Members of
3
4
the Council shall not be compensated for their service but shall
4
5
qualify for reimbursement for travel expenses under the State Travel
5
6
Reimbursement Act.
6
7
SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
